Hey everyone,

I'm Max, and I work in the Content team at SumUp, a Berlin-based fintech. We're active in a fair few places now, including most of Europe, the US, and Brazil. I mostly write product content and usually in blog format, and occasionally I write business guide articles and help with things like email marketing campaigns. I've been at SumUp for about four months now, and Berlin for 2 years.

text: Hi all! My name is Angeliki and I am managing content for a (pretty weird) Nordic think tank and consultancy called Demos Helsinki. Our job is to build a fair, sustainable and joyful agenda for the future. While we may not be in software/saas/tech, we work with a lot of the biggest tech companies and platforms (including Google) to translate their business goals into societal benefits. Still, a lot of our work and “thought leadership” aren’t communicated publicly, which is what I’m trying to improve in my role. This is how I found this thriving community! Looking forward to chatting more :cherry_blossom:
